title: Is It Weird That Her Parents Still Have Access To Her Finances?
description:
Our intern Darrian is in her 20s, and her parents still have access to her finances. At first, it didn't bother her, but now it's getting out of control. Her dad watches EVERYTHING she does. So what can she do to set up boundaries with her parents?
